Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵）王騎だ！ 王騎が来るぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.23,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Foot soldiers, forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵）歩兵 前へ！ 槍(やり) 構え！\N（趙兵）殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.91,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Have your spears at the ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.37,0:03:37.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）王騎自ら先陣を切るとき\Nその軍は全員 鬼神と化す
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:34.15,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,When Wang Qi was personally cutting through the vanguard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:37.15,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,his entire army turned into fierce deities!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N陣形の乱れた趙(ちょう)軍にとっては―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.41,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,And for the Zhao Army, whose formations had been thrown into disorder,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:46.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なおさら\Nそれを食い止めるすべはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:46.66,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,they had all the less ability to stop their charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:50.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえぞ！ 王騎軍の騎馬隊は！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:50.77,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Incredible! Check out the Wang Qi Army's mounted unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:53.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平(びへい)）\Nウオ～ッ！ 王騎将軍 万歳！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.79,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Hooray for General Wang Qi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:59.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）一方 王騎将軍の出現で\N救われた形となった蒙武(もうぶ)たちは―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:59.04,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Meng Wu and the others that were saved by the appearance of Wang Qi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.56,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,stayed where they were and watched over the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その場にとどまり\N戦を静観していた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:09.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（隆国(りゅうこく)）違う…\N（軍長）どうしましたか 隆国どの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.16,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.26,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lord Long Guo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:12.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（隆国）\Nこの戦い方は いつもの殿ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:12.31,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,This is not Lord's usual method of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.32,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,What is going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:14.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（隆国）どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:19.60,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,Why is Lord forcibly accelerating the war like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:19.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ殿は\Nこうも強引に戦を急がれるのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:22.20,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Change formations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:25.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,陣形を変える\N本陣を後ろへ下げるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.35,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Send the headquarters back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:28.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘の副官）\Nはっ！ 後退だ！ 後退する！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:28.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Retreat! We're retreating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:33.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎め…\N序盤にして 自ら先陣を切るだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:32.71,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,That Wang Qi... At the opening of the battle, you're cutting through the vanguard yourself? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焦らずとも 背後を断崖で\N囲まれている我々は逃げはせぬのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:38.39,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,We won't panic and with our rear surrounded by cliffs, we will not run away. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をそんなに急いでいる？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:40.09,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,Why is he rushing so much...? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.20,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,Could it be?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか 気づいているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.50,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,He's realized?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧(りぼく)）とにかく山あいに入ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.48,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,Anyhow, once you've entered the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:55.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで\N王騎将軍を呼び込んでください
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:55.14,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,call the Wang Qi Army here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:59.65,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,If you do that, the troops I've prepared for an ambush will head there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:59.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすれば\Nあとは私の用意した伏兵が向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.30,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,It's a simple plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…という単純な作戦です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.45,Kingdom-Flashback,Zhao,0,0,0,,Great General Li Mu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:08.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘）李牧 …大将軍\N（李牧）あっ はい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.33,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハッ…\Nその呼ばれ方は慣れませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.42,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,I'm not really used to being called that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘）将軍のおっしゃることは\N全て理解はできますが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Zhao,0,0,0,,I understand everything you have said, general.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:20.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮説に仮説を積み重ね過ぎていて\N正直 納得は しかねます
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:19.95,Kingdom-Flashback,Zhao,0,0,0,,By piling so many hypotheticals upon hypotheticals, I am reluctant to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも 秦に侵攻する際―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:26.50,Kingdom-Flashback,Zhao,0,0,0,,To begin with, what exactly is the likelihood that Wang Qi will appear when we invade Qin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:26.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎が出てくる可能性は\Nいかばかりか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（公孫龍(こうそんりゅう)）\N確かに 仮に王騎が来るとして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.18,Kingdom-Flashback,Long,0,0,0,,Indeed. Even if Wang Qi does come,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将軍がおっしゃる必勝の策が\Nヤツに通じるとは―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:33.18,Kingdom-Flashback,Long,0,0,0,,the certain-victory plan that you are speaking of will work against him, general...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:35.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念ながら 思えませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:35.18,Kingdom-Flashback,Long,0,0,0,,But I'm afraid I cannot believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（公孫龍）\Nあとで参戦するとのことでしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:38.15,Kingdom-Flashback,Long,0,0,0,,You said they would join the war later on,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:42.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら何でも 万単位の\N軍を起こして 南下させれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:42.32,Kingdom-Flashback,Long,0,0,0,,but if we raise an army of over 100,000 and send them South,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず王騎は気づくはず
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.81,Kingdom-Flashback,Long,0,0,0,,Wang Qi is sure to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:49.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧）気づきませんよ　現に\Nあなた方も気づいてないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.61,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,He won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.20,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,In reality, even the two of you didn't notice, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:54.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先日 北部で13万の軍が結集し
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:55.04,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,A few days ago in the North, I gathered together an army of 130,000
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.71,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,and crushed the Xiongnu Army of 200,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,匈奴(きょうど)軍20万を撃破しました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:06:00.00,Kingdom-Flashback,Long,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんですと？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:04.19,Kingdom-Flashback,Zhao,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous! I haven't heard anything about such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:04.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな！\Nそんな話は聞いておりませんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:06.42,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,I'm enacting an information blockade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:09.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧）情報封鎖しているんですよ\N“情報操作”と言ってもよいですが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.91,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,Or you could call it information manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:16.85,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,By the way, I've just leaked the information that Mr. Pang Nuan is Supreme Commander of Zhao to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちなみに 王騎将軍には―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:17.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖さんが趙の総大将になるという\N情報だけを漏らしてあります
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:20.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧）そうすれば\N彼は必ず出てくるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:20.56,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,That is sure to draw him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:23.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,因縁がありますから\N（公孫龍）因縁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.94,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,They have a connection, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.44,Kingdom-Flashback,Long,0,0,0,,Connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:26.41,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,It's all right, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:28.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫ですよ お２方　この戦は…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:30.86,Kingdom-Flashback,Mu,0,0,0,,We are sure... to win this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず勝てます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:37.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突然 現れた\N李牧と名乗る新しい三大天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:37.53,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,That new Great Diva that appeared out of the blue, the man that calls himself Li Mu... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:43.21,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,Though everything he predicted has indeed come true... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:43.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 彼の予言したことは\N全て現実のものとなった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:46.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,李牧の指示どおり 北の軍の存在は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:48.21,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,Just as Li Mu instructed, no one knows of the existence of the northern army
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:49.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と公孫龍以外\N誰にも知られていない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.72,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,except for Gongsun Long and I. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:56.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,李白(りはく)や馮忌(ふうき) 自軍の将校たちですら\N知らなかった この事実
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:56.72,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,Even Li Bai and Feng Ji, our own commissioned officers, did not know that fact... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の王騎が知りうるはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.86,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,There is no way that the enemy, Wang Qi, would know it! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（軍長）歩兵隊 全軍 突撃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:05.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All foot soldier units, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オオッ… 左軍が前に出たぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.90,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,The left army went forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:19.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？ くそ！ 囮(おとり)の役目が\N終わった俺らは 出番なしかよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What?! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.68,0:07:19.73,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,With our role as decoys over, are we never gonna get a chance in the spotlight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:23.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（軍長）歩兵ども 隊列を整えよ！\N（尾平）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.88,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Foot soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.57,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Get in formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（軍長）よいか？ これより\Nこの軍は敵本陣を目指して…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.67,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:27.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,This army's target is the enemy headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:31.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突撃する！\N（兵士たち）ウオーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！ そう来なくっちゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Now we're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.69,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy foot soldiers just started advancing as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:40.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘の副官）前方 敵歩兵も前進\N秦軍は 全軍 攻撃の構えです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.13,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The entire Qin Army is in attack formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:45.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ａ）バカな！ 開戦早々に\Nこんな大博打(おおばくち)に出るとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.57,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:46.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,To plunge in with such a big gamble this early in the battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:47.73,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Has Wang Qi gone mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎は正気か？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不自然すぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:50.70,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,It's too unnatural. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:55.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり ヤツは気づいているのだ\N三大天 李牧の作戦を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.88,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,I knew it, he has realized it! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.20,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,Great Diva Li Mu's strategy... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:08:00.04,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But Wang Qi had not realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:08:00.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）ところが\N王騎は気づいてはいなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:04.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それほど 李牧の施した情報封鎖は\N完璧(かんぺき)だったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.49,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The information blockade that Li Mu had gone so far to put in place was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 王騎は この時点で―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.01,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But at this point, Wang Qi predicted
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:11.67,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,that there were troops ready for an ambush somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:11.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこかに趙軍の伏兵がいることを\N予想していた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,察したのは\Nこの決戦の地に着いたときだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:15.38,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,He sensed it when he reached this land of the deciding battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:20.86,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,At a glance, this bell-shaped area seems to have the Zhao Army backed into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:20.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この釣り鐘状の地は 一見\N趙軍を追い詰めた形に見えるが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:27.40,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,500)\pos(777.6,127)}Zhao Army
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:27.40,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,500)\pos(643.2,389.4)}Qin Army
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:26.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろから別の趙軍が来れば 今度は\N秦軍が追い詰められることとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.58,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But if a different Zhao Army came from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:27.40,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,500)\pos(505.4,520.6)}Zhao Army
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.92,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,then it would be the Qin Army with nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし そのころ\N山間部では秦軍の軍長たちが―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:32.48,Kingdom-Main,Narration,0,0,0,,But as this was happening, the Qin Army military commanders were holding back different Zhao Armies among the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:32.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それぞれ\Nほかの趙軍を押さえていた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.88,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Push them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:38.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁(へき)）押し戻せ！\Nこの地を死守するのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.88,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,We must protect this ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）各軍長の奮戦により―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.44,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,With the hard fights against each military commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:46.85,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,at a glance, there didn't seem to be any Zhao Army that could attack Wang Qi's group's rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:47.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一見すれば 王騎たちの\N背を取る趙軍はあるはずがなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.77,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし “自分の見えていない敵が\Nこの山中にいる”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:53.33,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,There is an enemy invisible to him in these mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何者かが現れると想定したとき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.96,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,When he predicted that someone may appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:59.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎には 趙の本陣が 山へ\N入ったとき以来 抱えていた―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:09:01.28,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,the answers to the suspicions Wang Qi had since the enemy headquarters had entered the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:02.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,疑念の答えが明確に出た
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.57,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,became clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:08.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこから王騎の思考は 前に進む
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:08.06,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,From there, Wang Qi's thinking progressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:13.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎は\N本陣の旗の範囲を越えてからは―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.97,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,After Wang Qi went outside the range of his headquarters' flags,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:16.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,進みながら敵の居場所を探っている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.12,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,he investigated the enemy's location as he moved forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:20.65,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Zhao Army's ambush troops were not caught by those search units.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:20.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙軍の伏兵は\Nその捜索部隊に引っ掛かっていない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:25.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だろう\Nここまで周到に策を巡らす敵である
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:26.31,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Of course, this is an enemy that was utterly meticulous in their planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:31.25,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The reinforcements were all dispersed and lying in wait outside the area of Wang Qi's search.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:31.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,援軍は必ず 王騎の捜索の範囲外に\N分散して伏せてあるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:35.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで逆に 山という場所が\N趙軍に 裏目に出る
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:35.76,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,But here, the mountain location actually backfired against the Zhao Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:45.84,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Because Wang Qi had confidence that he could end the war before the ambush troops arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:45.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎には 伏兵が到着する前に\N決着をつける自信があったのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:51.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）フフフッ…\Nどこのどなたか知りませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.84,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,I don't know who or where they are, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い仕掛けです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:53.96,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,but this is an interesting setup. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:58.96,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,However, the endgame was taken a bit too lightly. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:10:01.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 少々 詰めが甘かったですね\N私が その気になれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.12,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,If I feel like it... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:02.87,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wang Qi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵）王騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:09.50,Kingdom-Thought,Wang,0,0,0,,I can destroy the Zhao Zhuang Army in an instant. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:09.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,趙荘軍など瞬殺ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政(せい)）楊端和(ようたんわ)の情報にあった\N我々の知らぬ趙軍の伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:17.01,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,With the results of the Zhao Army ambush we learned of through Yang Duan He
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.67,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,the aim of the man named Li Mu is most likely something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:19.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,李牧という男のねらいは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく\Nこういうことだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:26.14,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)\move(721,247,1350,247)}Zhao Army {All Brown}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:26.14,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)\move(486,250,1130,250,)}Qin Army {Light brown}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:26.14,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,500)\move(265,247,930,247)}Zhao Army {All Brown}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:26.24,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,If I can predict it here in Xianyang,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）咸陽(かんよう)にいる俺が\N予想できることなら―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.14,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,500)\pos(378.6,117.4)}Zhao Army {All Brown}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.14,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,500)\pos(164.2,199)}Zhao Army {All Brown}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.14,Kingdom-Map,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,500)\pos(247.4,463)}Zhao Army {All Brown}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:28.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎も既に気づいているはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.35,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Wang Qi should have already realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:31.56,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,That man's experience and intuition on the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:31.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君(しょうぶんくん)）戦場における\Nあの男の経験と勘は―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:35.90,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,is certainly not inferior to some unheard-of man called Li Mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:35.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,李牧などという無名の男に\N負けるはずはありません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）だが 気になることがある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.81,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,But something bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:43.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ趙軍の総大将は\N龐煖という男なのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:43.00,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Why is Pang Nuan the Zhao Army's Supreme Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.91,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Just as you told me earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:45.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,以前 お前が申したとおり―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:49.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖が 人を率いるたぐいの\N武将でないならば―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:49.93,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,if Pang Nuan is not the kind of military general that leads men,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:53.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“総大将”という肩書は\Nむしろ不釣り合いではないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:53.72,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,then the title of Supreme Commander is rather unfitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:54.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,た… 確かに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:54.92,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,Y-You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:11:01.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか 李牧は全てを知ったうえで\N龐煖を総大将に担いだというのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:58.85,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Could it be that Li Mu knew all of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:01.43,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,and made Pang Nuan carry the title of Supreme Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:04.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をしている！ 王騎を止めよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.59,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:04.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop Wang Qi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大天旗を動かせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:07.99,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Move the Great Diva Flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:11.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後軍を前に出し 防御陣を作れ！\N後退だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.46,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Move the rear army forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:11.68,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,create a defensive formation! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:13.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ａ）趙荘さま！ 趙荘さま！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:12.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Zhao Zhuang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Zhao Zhuang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.64,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ａ）ほ… 龐煖さまが…\N龐煖さまがいません！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:19.16,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,L-Lord Pang Nuan... Lord Pang Nuan is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:22.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？\Nカイシン！ 龐煖さまは どこだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.32,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,What?! Jie Shen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.96,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Where is Lord Pang Nuan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:26.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わ… 分かりませぬ！\N先ほどまで目の前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:24.94,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,I-I do not know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.94,0:11:26.42,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,He was right in front of me a moment ago...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アア… まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:29.33,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵）\N現在 本陣付近 隊形を変形中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:38.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They're currently changing formations near the headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:42.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとしても ここで食い止めねば\N（セイウ）分かっておる！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.29,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We have to stop them here, or...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.25,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:47.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かっておる …が どうやったら\Nあれを止められる？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.47,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I know... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.23,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,how do we stop {\i1}that{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Qing Yu! Wang Qi is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵）\Nセイウさま 王騎が来ます！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵）セイウさま 命令を！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.35,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Qing Yu, your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:58.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,憎き秦の六大将軍 王騎\Nウワサ以上のバケモノだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:56.46,Kingdom-Main,Qing,0,0,0,,The hated Wang Qi of Qin's Six Great Generals...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.40,Kingdom-Main,Qing,0,0,0,,He is more of a monster than the rumors foretold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:41.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァハァ… な… 何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.40,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騰(とう)）うん？\N（部下Ｂ）騰さま これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.75,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Teng, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:46.41,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What's going on?! The front lines are shouting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘の副官）\N何だ？ 前線で喚声(かんせい)が！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖さまだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.91,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,It's Lord Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:17.23,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,Do you think, my king... that Li Mu knows of the connection between Wang Qi and Pang Nuan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:17.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）まさか 大王… 李牧は\N王騎と龐煖の因縁を知っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あえて龐煖を総大将にしたと？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.90,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,so he went so far as to make Pang Nuan the Supreme Commander...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:24.04,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Most likely he is Supreme Commander in name alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:21.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）恐らく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“総大将”とは名目だけで―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:27.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖は 王騎を\N戦場に引きずり出すためのエサ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:27.24,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan is simply bait meant to lure Wang Qi to the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）最後の六大将軍 王騎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.50,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,The last of the Six Great Generals, Wang Qi... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:37.12,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,He is a man feared as the Mystery Bird of the State of Qin, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“秦国の怪鳥”と恐れられながら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっときは\N戦を捨てたとまで思われた男
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.79,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,but was also thought to have given up on war for a time... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 龐煖なる存在は\Nそれを再び戦場に引き戻した
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:45.76,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,However, the being known as Pang Nuan was able to bring him back to the battlefield. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:49.68,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Just what reason would drive Wang Qi that far...? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:50.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎をそこまで駆り立てる理由は\N一体 何なのだ？ やはり…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.22,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,That must be it. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昌文君\N（昌文君）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:52.22,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,Changwenjun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.34,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:57.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖に倒された六大将軍 摎(きょう)とは\N何者なのだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:57.53,Kingdom-Main,Zhang,0,0,0,,Who exactly was Liao, the member of the Six Great Generals that was defeated by Pang Nuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:14:03.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎にとって 摎は 何か\N特別な存在だったのではないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:03.36,Kingdom-Main,Zhang,0,0,0,,Liao was a special person to Wang Qi somehow, is that not true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）\Nンフフフッ… ９年ぶりですか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:12.87,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Has it really been 9 years...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:19.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやく会えましたねえ 龐煖\Nお元気でしたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:18.47,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,We finally meat again... Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:19.83,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.24,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）しかし 驚きましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:28.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てっきり死んだものとばかり\N思っていたあなたが―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:28.61,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,I had always been certain you were dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:33.72,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,but then I see you appearing as a Supreme Commander of over 100,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:34.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突然 10万を超える大軍の\N総大将になって現れるんですからね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつから道化に？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.60,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,So when did you become a clown?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:40.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（龐煖）手段など小事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.04,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,The means are a trifling matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:44.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるのは武神の証明 ただひとつ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:44.15,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,All that matters is my proof of being a War God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:53.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎… 貴様をここで殺して\N我が武神たるを天に指し示す！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.04,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,Wang Qi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:53.62,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,I will kill you here and show the heavens that I am a War God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:57.12,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,I am as relieved as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お変わりなくて 安心しましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:58.85,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:58.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:15.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）私も ここで…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.06,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,I believe I will be the one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:24.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたを殺して 過去のしがらみと\N決別することを宣言しましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:24.02,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,to kill {\i1}you{\i0} here and declare that I have broken from the fetters of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:27.03,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:28.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ？\N（龐煖）ンッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:32.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくぞ 王騎！ お前を殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:30.19,Kingdom-Main,Pang Nuan,0,0,0,,Here we go, Wang Qi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.99,Kingdom-Main,Pang Nuan,0,0,0,,I will... kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:40.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンフフフッ…\N私のセリフですよ 龐煖！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:40.21,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,That is my line, Pang Nuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.83,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It-It's finally begun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:46.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つ… ついに始まる\N大将同士の一騎打ちが
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.30,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The one-on-one fight between Supreme Commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵たち）龐煖さま！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.43,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Lord Pang Nuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:48.30,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Lord Wang Qi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎軍兵たち）殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:15:59.47,Kingdom-Thought,Guys,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:08.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.49,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,H-He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:13.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意外と軽いんですねえ 龐煖さん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:13.74,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,You're surprisingly light, Mr. Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:22.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）この盛り上がりは…\N（田有(でんゆう)）王騎将軍と龐煖か
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.75,Kingdom-Main,Qin,0,0,0,,What's this uproar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.79,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Do you think it's General Wang Qi and Pan Nuan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.04,Kingdom-Main,Qin,0,0,0,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:26.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いねえ\Nくそ… こうしちゃいられねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.27,Kingdom-Main,Qin,0,0,0,,Shit! Why do we have to be doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（軍長）\N歩兵ども！ 足を止めるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:28.86,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Foot soldiers, do not stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:32.01,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Our goal is the Zhao Army headquarters alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:32.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々の目的は\Nあくまで趙軍の本陣！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全軍を指揮する趙荘を\N討つことである！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.60,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We will kill the one directing all units, Zhao Zhuang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:41.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全軍 前進！ 進め！\N（兵士たち）へ～い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:39.25,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All units, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:44.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どの！\N（尾平）信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:42.98,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.08,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ンッ… 羌瘣(きょうかい)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:46.61,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:50.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎将軍と龐煖\Nどっちが強(つえ)えと思う？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:50.11,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Which do you think is stronger, General Wang Qi or Pang Nuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣）龐煖\N（去亥(きょがい)）ふざけんな てめえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:54.83,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:57.15,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Quit screwing around, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:17:00.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんてこと言うんだよ！\Nそれでも秦軍か？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:00.50,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,How could you say that? And you call yourself a member of the Qin Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:03.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら 聞くな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.42,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Then don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:08.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪(はいろう)）\Nヤツのせいで 大勢 仲間を失った
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.79,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Because of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.25,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,we lost quite a few comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:16.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　俺らにゃ 龐煖の最期を\N見届ける資格は十分あるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:16.15,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That's right. We are plenty qualified to see Pang Nuan's end for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:16.87,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:22.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（松左(しょうさ)）確か俺たちは\N王騎将軍の直下の特殊部隊だよな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:22.96,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,We are a special unit working directly under General Wang Qi, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:26.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永(でんえい)）\N将軍から受けた命令は陽動だけだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:26.06,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,The only orders we were given by the general was to cause a diversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.18,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Meaning now, we're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は自由かと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:39.10,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:42.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし！ 飛信(ひしん)隊 俺に続け！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:42.29,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Feixin Unit! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:11.12,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,He's strong. General Wang Qi is even stronger than Pang Nuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:11.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）\N強い… 王騎将軍は龐煖より強いぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）我らの殿に敵はない！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.98,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Our lord is unparalleled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:16.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）コウロウさま これは…\N（コウロウ）うん…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Huang Nou, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:21.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで９年前の 摎さまと龐煖の\N戦いを見ているようじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:21.03,Kingdom-Main,Huang,0,0,0,,It's like I'm seeing the battle between Lord Liao and Pang Nuan from 9 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:28.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのときも そうじゃった　龐煖は\N相手の力を存分に引き出してから…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.93,Kingdom-Main,Huang,0,0,0,,It was like this then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:27.63,Kingdom-Main,Huang,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan thoroughly brought out his enemy's power, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:31.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気を出す
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:31.00,Kingdom-Main,Huang,0,0,0,,he got... serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.31,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,Holding back will get you nowhere... Wang Qi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:43.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（龐煖）出し惜しみは無用 王騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだまだ\Nこんなものではないはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.31,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,This should not be all you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろんですよ ンフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.39,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:05.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Wh-What an incredible battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.98,0:19:07.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）す… すごい戦いだ\N（兵士）２人の矛の動きが見えぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.54,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I can't even see their lances' movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖のほうが やや優勢か\N（コウロウ）殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:18.69,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Does Pang Nuan have a slight advantage...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:19.09,Kingdom-Main,Huang,0,0,0,,Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:20.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵）見ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:23.51,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Look! The hated Wang Qi is bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵）\Nあの憎き王騎が血を流している！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:27.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙兵）ああ　龐煖さまは お強い\N（趙兵）お強いぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:26.12,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Yes! Lord Pang Nuan is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.12,0:19:27.19,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,He truly is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:36.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘の副官）このまま本陣を\N後ろへ下げる　隊列を乱すな！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.61,Kingdom-Main,Vice,0,0,0,,Continue to send the headquarters backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:36.61,Kingdom-Main,Vice,0,0,0,,Do not break rank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:41.20,Kingdom-Thought,Zhao,0,0,0,,If Wang Qi is accepting this one-on-one match, then... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:41.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの王騎が\Nこのような一騎打ちに応じるとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ｃ）趙荘さま！\N（趙荘）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.20,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Zhao Zhuang!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:46.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ｃ）今は\N龐煖さまが王騎と一騎打ちの最中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:46.70,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Pang Nuan is currently engaged in a one-on-one battle with Wang Qi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:49.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣を下げてもよろしいのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.15,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Are you sure we should send the headquarters back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:52.28,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The winner of their match will determine the winner of this war!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:52.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（部下Ｄ）\N２人の勝敗は そのまま戦の勝敗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:55.29,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Is there still meaning in drawing the headquarters back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣を下げる意味は？\N（趙荘）そう単純ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.09,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,It's not that simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:02.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我が軍の頂点は 龐煖さまではなく\N俺を中心とした―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:20:00.74,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,The top of our army is not Lord Pang Nuan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:04.76,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,it is this headquarters with me at the center. Do not forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:05.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この本陣であることを忘れるな\N（部下たち）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仮に\N龐煖さまが王騎を討ったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:08.57,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,And even if Lord Pang Nuan defeats Wang Qi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとき\Nこの本陣が討たれていれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:13.10,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,if this headquarters falls after that, we will not be able to adapt to the Qin Army's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦軍の動きに対応できぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.92,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,The opposite is equally true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:17.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘）逆もまたしかり\N龐煖さまが もし討たれても―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:17.70,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,If Lord Pang Nuan is killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:20.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この本陣が生きていれば\N立て直しが図れる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.61,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,as long as this headquarters lives, we can plan a regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:26.12,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,In order for them to win this war, they need to defeat the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:26.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツらが戦で我が軍に勝つのは\Nこの本陣を討つことが必要なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:30.19,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Wang Qi knows that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:30.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして\N王騎も そのことを知っている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:34.03,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,That is why that mounted unit is not headed to Wang Qi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:33.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから あの騎馬隊は\N王騎のもとに駆けつけず
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.67,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,it is coming towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらに向かってくるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（趙荘）\N気をつけろ　あれは手ごわいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:39.15,Kingdom-Main,Zhao,0,0,0,,Be careful. They are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（飛信隊員）あっ どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:44.87,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.34,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,I feel bad for the other foot soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:51.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの歩兵のヤツらに悪かったかな\N俺らだけ戦わず 観戦なんて…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:51.77,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,We're the only just observing instead of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:55.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ言え　いざとなったら\Nここが いちばんの―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.16,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:57.49,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,If shit hits the fan, this place will become the most blood-splattered battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:59.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血みどろの乱戦場になるんだぞ\N（尾平）そ… そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:58.90,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,I-I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:01.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもんは どうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:01.41,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:05.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は とにかく\N王騎将軍と龐煖の一騎打ちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:02.40,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What's important now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:05.37,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,is General Wang Qi and Pang Nuan's one-on-one fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.92,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,General Wang Qi is being pushed back?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:18.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王騎将軍が押されてんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:21.21,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Pang Nuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,龐煖！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:30.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身に受けた傷の痛みは\N時と共に消え去る
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:29.97,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,The pain from wounds suffered by the body eventually disappear with time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:35.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 魂に受けた傷の痛みは\N消え去ることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:35.59,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,But pain from wounds suffered by the soul will never disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:37.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何年たとうとも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:37.69,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,No matter how many years go by...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:43.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（龐煖）王騎！ お前も同じはずだ\Nだから お前も ここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:40.73,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,Wang Qi, it should be the same for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.74,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,That is why you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,怒りは力…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:46.20,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,Anger is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:50.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も思い出せ\N９年前のヤツの死にザマを！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.49,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,You must remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:51.20,Kingdom-Main,Pang,0,0,0,,the sight of that one's death 9 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.24,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,He cut him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,斬った！\N（セイウ）龐煖さま！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:21:59.21,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Pang Nuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士たち）王騎将軍！\N（歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.74,Kingdom-Main,People,0,0,0,,Long live General Wang Qi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:08.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:08.48,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,That one? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:13.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王騎）\Nンフフフッ… 安心しなさい 龐煖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.72,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Rest easy, Pang Nuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:20.30,Kingdom-Main,Wang,0,0,0,,Just like you, my wounds have not healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたと同様\N私の傷も癒えてはいませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:25.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）分かりました\N全てをお話しいたしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:22.98,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:25.24,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,I will tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:27.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,摎について その素性が―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:31.24,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,There is a reason why Liao's background is so unnaturally not known.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:31.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不自然なほど知られていないのには\N訳があります
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.73,0:22:34.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昭王(しょうおう)が禁じたのです\N（政）昭王が？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.86,0:22:33.94,Kingdom-Main,Changwen,0,0,0,,King Zhao forbid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:34.74,Kingdom-Main,Zheng,0,0,0,,King Zhao?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:39.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君）あの者が\N抱えていた秘密は 大変 複雑でした
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:39.50,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,The secrets that person held were incredibly complex...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:42.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし今 重要なことは―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:46.76,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,But now what's important is that Liao was an extremely important person to Wang Qi.
