Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:02.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,女でした
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:01.70,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,was a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:05.25,Kingdom-Main,Chang,0,0,0,,And Liao was...
